{"tid":533853,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩霸氣得過三百蚊買個手機殻用都未用過就屈爛佢掉落垃圾桶","createTime":"2018-01-19T08:34:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T13:29:59.000Z","uid":159183,"like":6,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7fcb63cf49a3d921b02178380e73aea65d9ef737","tid":533853,"uid":159183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T08:34:39.000Z","msg":"有咩霸氣得過三百蚊買個手機殻用都未用過就屈爛佢掉落垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩買左個air jacket殻<br />\n298hkd<br />\n好多巴打都用緊 我見幾靚就去買黎試下<br />\n點知岩岩返到屋企一開 仆佢個街有條勁明顯嘅花痕係相機位果到（買果時個盒遮住哂睇唔到）<br />\n諗住搵塊布抹下佢睇下有冇好轉<br />\n唔抹又自可 一抹把幾火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抹完花痕冇消失不突只 仲多左好多條細嘅花痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個下即刻勁燥底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時返工壓力已經大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要咁樣黎玩鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屈鳩爛左個殻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/163437_b497416b80db185f51d2856e439e54e0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F163437_b497416b80db185f51d2856e439e54e0.png&h=06d6b1ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96e129276a3e8da4b6b3050b38648f999bd5f6ea","tid":533853,"uid":3122,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T08:36:18.000Z","msg":"傻西"},{"pid":"1758917796c681dac5776e7ef8ac26cefd353ad6","tid":533853,"uid":36136,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T08:36:30.000Z","msg":"2017/10/10"},{"pid":"cd109c9c1ff89ff0b92bb2c0535e2528c390ddbe","tid":533853,"uid":159183,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"1758917796c681dac5776e7ef8ac26cefd353ad6","tid":533853,"uid":